# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CCGNF grammar engine — generated and intermediate outputs (future)
#
# The grammar is implemented via ANTLR code generation; generated C# sources
# land under src/Ccgnf/generated/ (gitignored, regenerated per build). The
# preprocessor and validator produce per-file intermediates; these go to
# *.ccgnf.expanded siblings or into .ccgnf-cache/.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
src/Ccgnf/generated/
src/Ccgnf/Generated/
**/generated/antlr/
*.ccgnf.expanded
*.ccgnf.validated
.ccgnf-cache/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Web frontend (Vite + TypeScript) under web/.
#
# Build artifacts are produced by `make web-build` and copied into
# src/Ccgnf.Rest/wwwroot/. The web/dist/ directory itself is unused (build
# writes directly to wwwroot/), but ignore it defensively in case of
# one-off vite builds without the --outDir override.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
web/node_modules/
web/dist/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Card-cluster skill working files
#
# `working-*.ccgnf` files are in-flight cluster drafts. Only `cluster-*.ccgnf`
# (finalized archives with a known seed and approved contents) get committed.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
encoding-artifacts/working-*.ccgnf
